\c 24
\nb
\v 1 UBalami esebonile ukuthi kuhle emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* ukubusisa uIsrayeli, kahambanga njengezinye izikhathi ukuyadinga imilingo\x + 23.3,15.\x*; kodwa wakhangelisa ubuso bakhe enkangala.
\v 2 Kwathi uBalami ephakamisa amehlo akhe, wabona uIsrayeli ehlezi ngokwezizwe zakhe\x + 2.2-31.\x*, loMoya kaNkulunkulu waba phezu kwakhe\x + Hlu. 3.10; 1 Sam. 19.20,23. 2 Lan. 15.1; 20.14.\x*.
\v 3 Wasephakamisa umfanekiso wakhe wathi: UBalami indodana kaBeyori\x + 2 Sam. 23.1.\x* uthi, lendoda olihlo layo livulekile ithi,
\v 4 uthi ozwayo amazwi kaNkulunkulu, obonayo umbono kaSomandla, esiwa, njalo kwembulwe amehlo\x + 1 Sam. 19.24. Hez. 1.28; 3.23? Isam. 1.10,17.\x*.
\v 5 Mahle kangakanani amathente akho, Jakobe, amakhaya akho, Israyeli!
\v 6 Njengezigodi zisabalele, njengezivande ngasemfuleni, njengezinhlaba\x + Hlab. 1.3. Jer. 17.8.\x* iN\nd kosi\nd* ezihlanyeleyo, njengezihlahla zemisedari ngasemanzini\x + Hlab. 104.16.\x*!
\v 7 Amanzi azageleza evela embizeni zakhe, lenhlanyelo yakhe izakuba semanzini amanengi\x + Jer. 51.13. Isam. 17.1.\x*, lenkosi yakhe izakuba nkulu kuloAgagi\x + 24.20. 1 Sam. 15.8.\x*, lombuso wakhe uzaphakama\x + 2 Sam. 5.12. 1 Lan. 14.2.\x*.
\v 8 UNkulunkulu wamkhupha eGibhithe, ulokunjengamandla enyathi\x + 23.22.\x*, uzakudla izizwe, izitha zakhe\x + 14.9; 23.24.\x*, njalo uzakwephula amathambo azo\x + Hez. 23.34; Isa. 38.13. Jer. 50.17.\x*, njalo azitshoke ngemitshoko yakhe\x + 24.17. Hlab. 45.5. Jer. 50.9.\x*.
\v 9 Waqutha, walala phansi njengesilwane, lanjengesilwane esisikazi; ngubani ozamvusa?\x + Gen. 49.9. Nani 23.24.\x* Okubusisayo abusiswe, lokuqalekisayo aqalekiswe!\x + Gen. 12.3; 27.29.\x*
\p
\v 10 Njalo ulaka lukaBalaki lwavuthela uBalami, watshaya izandla zakhe\x + Hez. 21.12. Jobe 27.23. Lilo 2.15.\x*, uBalaki wasesithi kuBalami: Ngikubize ukuze uqalekise izitha zami, kodwa khangela, uzibusisile lokuzibusisa\x + 23.11.\x* okwalezizikhathi ezintathu.
\v 11 Khathesi-ke zibalekele uye endaweni yakho. Bengithe ngizakuhlonipha ngodumo, kodwa khangela, iN\nd kosi\nd* ikuvimbile kudumo\x + 22.17,37.\x*.
\v 12 UBalami wasesithi kuBalaki: Kangikhulumanga yini lakuzithunywa obuzithume kimi ngisithi:
\v 13 Uba uBalaki ebezangipha indlu yakhe igcwele isiliva legolide, bengingayikweqa umlayo weN\nd kosi\x + 22.18.\x*\nd*, ukwenza okuhle kumbe okubi okwenhliziyo yami; lokho iN\nd kosi\nd* ekutshoyo yilokho engizakukhuluma?\x + 16.28.\x*
\v 14 Khathesi-ke, khangela, ngiya ebantwini bakithi; woza ngikucebise ukuthi lababantu bazakwenzani ebantwini bakini\x + Mika 6.5\x* ensukwini zokucina\x + Gen. 49.1. Dan. 10.14.\x*.
\p
\v 15 Wasephakamisa umfanekiso wakhe wathi\x + 24.3,20,23; 21.27; 23.7.\x*: UBalami indodana kaBeyori\x + 24.3,4.\x* uthi, lendoda elamehlo avulekileyo ithi,
\v 16 uthi ozwayo amazwi kaNkulunkulu\x + 24.3,4.\x*, lowazi ulwazi loPhezukonke, obonayo umbono kaSomandla, esiwa, njalo kuvuleke amehlo.
\v 17 Ngizambona, kodwa hatshi khathesi\x + 23.9.\x*, ngizamkhangela, kodwa kungeseduze\x + 23.9.\x*; kuzavela\x + Jobe 9.8. Mika 1.3.\x* inkanyezi kuJakobe\x + Mat. 2.2. Isam. 22.16.\x*, lentonga yobukhosi izavuka koIsrayeli\x + Gen. 49.10.\x*, itshaye amagumbi akoMowabi, njalo ichithe bonke abantwana bakaShethi.
\v 18 Njalo uEdoma uzakuba yimfuyo\x + 2 Sam. 8.14. Hlab. 60.8,9,12.\x*, loSeyiri abe yimfuyo yezitha zakhe\x + Gen. 32.3.\x*, kodwa uIsrayeli uzakwenza ngobuqhawe\x + Gen.15.19.\x*,
\v 19 kuzavela-ke koJakobe umbusi, njalo uzabhubhisa oseleyo emzini.
\p
\v 20 Esebone uAmaleki, waphakamisa umfanekiso wakhe wathi:
\p UAmaleki wayengowokuqala wezizwe, kodwa ukucina kwakhe kuyikubhubha okupheleleyo.
\p
\v 21 Esebone amaKeni, waphakamisa umfanekiso wakhe wathi:
\p Iqinile indlu yakho, isidleke sakho usimise edwaleni.
\v 22 Kanti-ke uKhayini uzachithwa, aze akuthumbe uAshuri.
\p
\v 23 Wasephakamisa umfanekiso wakhe wathi: Maye, ngubani ozaphila nxa uNkulunkulu esenza lokhu?
\v 24 Imikhumbi izavela ekhunjini lweKitimi\x + Dan. 11.30. Gen. 10.4.\x*, ihluphe uAshuri, ihluphe uEberi\x + Gen. 10.21,25.\x*; njalo laye uzabhubha okwesikhathi sonke\x + 24.20.\x*.
\p
\v 25 UBalami wasesukuma wahamba wabuyela endaweni yakhe; loBalaki laye wahamba ngendlela yakhe\x + 31.8.\x*.
